      • retrieveTopKApps

        public ArrayList<TopKApp> retrieveTopKApps(Date startDateTime,
                                           Date endDateTime,
                                           String school,
                                           String topKValue)
        Retrieve Top K Apps given a start date, end date, school and top K value
        Parameters:
        startDateTime - the start date and time of the input field
        endDateTime - the end date and time of the input field
        school - selected school (SIS, Business, Economics, Accountancy, SOCSC, Law)
        topKValue - top K value chosen by user, where k can range from 1 to 10 (both inclusive, in integer increments)
        Returns:
        ArrayList ArrayList of TopKApp objects
